protected String getShortName(String name) {     if (name.startsWith("get")) {         name = Character.toLowerCase(name.charAt(3)) + name.substring(4).     } else if (name.startsWith("search") && !"search".equals(name)) {         name = Character.toLowerCase(name.charAt(6)) + name.substring(7).     }     return name. }
